column5: I can't go, but I thought I would post here for people to check out the hook up section if you want the chance to get the biggest walleye of your life this is a way to do it if you don't have a big enough boat or don't know how to fish for big walleye  click here Quinte walleye Hookups  guys if you are not checking out the other sections you are missing the boat
Brownie points for November, Terry?  It happens that Terry is dead on on this one though. Take his advice.
If LakerJessy would hurry up and have this baby...I'd be all over that!!!
I heard on the radio that theres a big algea bloom going on in the bay...

no I was keeping it a secret as I was hoping to go but now that I find I can't  go, others should get the chance  I always kick myself when I  find I missed something because I forget to check the other section and that's why I like only one section for everything  then I would miss nothing   and I do, GET BY WITH A LITTLE HELP FROM MY FRIENDS
The bloom is between Carrying Place and Deseronto... so shouldn't effect the area that we generally fish the BOQ for big pickeraleyes.
I'm the same Terry, I don't like to miss anything. I use the View New Posts function at the top of the page. At least the way I role.
You were just going to prefish.You cant fool me.LOL
I could use some pre fishing and post fishing    but mostly I need walleye fishing
What the heck did you do to the sub title Terry..
well what the heck is that I think I wrote this weekend on the second line??????LOL
I think Terry is a suck-  ... if it was that good he would make the time!!!
my wife tells me I am going to her family's place this weekend for the Canadian thanksgiving    suck.....you bet..you tell her I'm not going with her..not me
Did ya want me to give Dawg the phone number so you can claim it wasn't you Terry.....
I,ll just open the window and give a yell,,,,,,,   HEY MRS,S,TERRYS GOING FISHING.HE WILL SEE YOU WHEN HE GETS BACK.   There,that should make you safe bud.  No one else had the balls to do it.LOL
